10 creation or perpetuation of monopolies and practices detrimental to
11 the public welfare, to prevent the practice of requiring the buying
12 of special features, appliances and equipment not desired or
13 requested by the purchaser, to prevent false and misleading
14 advertising, to prevent unfair practices by new motor vehicle
15 dealers or, powersports vehicle dealers, manufacturers, factories,
